<h4>Comparing Wallets</h4>
<p>Every wallet comes with pros and cons. On one hand, we would recommend wallets like Coinbase wallet to new users because it is the beginner-friendly and offers a range of features. On the other hand, software wallets like Coinbase wallet inherit security vulnerabilities that could result in loss of user funds.</p>
<p>It's very important for new users to consider their options and risks when selecting a wallet. As a general best practice, we recommend NOT to store large amounts of money using with anything but a hardware wallet!</p>
<p>ELI5: Software wallets are hackable because your secret key is online. Hardware wallets are not hackable, because the secret key is only on the device.</p>



